📄 Project Proposal: Neon Merge — A Rust-Based Idle Merge Game
🧠 Executive Summary
Neon Merge is a stylized mobile idle-merge game set in a vibrant neon world of geometric shapes. Built using Rust and the Bevy game engine, the project aims to deliver high performance, modular architecture, and a scalable progression system.
The game combines:

Merge mechanics
Idle resource generation (“Aura”)
Upgrade systems
Prestige (Rebirth) and long-term Paragon progression

This project prioritizes:

Clean systems architecture
High performance
Long-term maintainability
Modern rendering techniques


🎮 Game Concept Overview
🌌 Theme & Art Direction

Neon-inspired world with electric blues and purples
Minimalist geometric shapes (25+ levels)
Glow effects, pulses, and energy flows
Clean, responsive UI

🔁 Core Gameplay Loop

Spawn geometric shapes on a grid
Merge identical shapes → evolve to higher tier
Generate Aura (primary currency)
Spend Aura on upgrades
Reinforce progression via:

Rebirth (reset loop)
Paragon system (persistent buffs)




